  Hit jit8 si7 long5-lek8 12 geh8 29 jit8, in e5 hiu-ka2-jit8. keh jit8 chiu7-si7 chiaN-geh8 chhoe 1. Goa2 e5 a-chek chiu7 khai-si2 heng5-tong7 lah. I koat-i3 ai3 beh koh ke3-siok8 pai3 put8,chiu7 kap bo5 sin3 Chu2 it-poaN e5 lang5 siang7-khoan2, tah lian5, kat-chhai2. Koh khi3 goa7-bin7 toa3 chin-choe7 ngou2-siong7 lai5 chhu3-nih beh hok8-sai7. 
